Daily: ISIS rival in Syria. OnionDog hits Korea. Ransomeware and DDoS. Remorse in Manitoba. 

Dave Larson, COO at Corero, shares his thoughts on DDoS attacks, and Jonathan Katz from the University of Maryland addresses recent healthcare ransomware attacks.
